snippet.title: Use your words.
snippet.description:
Reading about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Ain't that some shit, it's not even the domestic aspect, because we don't know what happens in people's homes behind closed doors. Just to go and destroy someone's name and career by lying about some serious allegations while making yourself a martyr is some shit. especially when you were in there throwing pots and pans. 

original video by Incredibly Average https://youtu.be/aca0KWoHtqQ
